Event.create(title:"Kung Fu Panda and Sushi", description:"We would like to formaly invite you to the screening of Kung Fu panda and a sushi evening extradorinaire. Now you may be thinking Kung fu and Pandas are of Chinese decent- yes we know, but we really love sushi and as such we will be serving home made sushi throughout the evening. Nakamote our Japanese friend will be giving a sushi making demo before the screening of our favourite movie Kung Fu Panda. We are thouroughly looking forward to showing our Japanese friend a Canadian good time so please come join us next week for what is sure to be a great event.",movie_genre:"Animation",cuisine:"Japanese",capacity: 15  ,price: 30  ,address:"123,  Garanvile Avenue",event_date:"2016-06-21",image_file:"kung-fu-panda.jpg",start_time:"20:00 PM ")
Event.create(title:"Imitation Game and international cuisine", description:"For us computer enthusiasts Alan Turin and his Turin machine is of particular interest. He and his team were able to shorten the war by two years by cracking the enigma code. Come explore this interesting story as we watch the Oscar award winning Imatation game. We will be offereing a selection of cuisines from around the world and truly hope to bring together people of different nationalties to celebrate a united world and the birth of the computing machine.",movie_genre:"Drama",cuisine:"Traditional",capacity: 10  ,price: 35  ,address:"456, Main Street",event_date:"2016-06-24",image_file:"imitation game.jpeg",start_time:"21:00 PM")
