Event.create(title:"The Hangover with a Greasy Feast", description:"At the Sadeh household we love a good party and hope you do to. We invite you to the Hangover (the movie) inspired evening with a greasy feast served throughout the night. Upon entry you will receive a bottle of beer and 2 shots of Jagermeister. At 8pm we will all sit down to enjoy the feature of the evening, while burgers, hotdogs and other greasy classics are served. We have a fully stocked bar and look forward to meeting new friends. Who knows where the night will lead. Wink wink.",movie_genre:"Comedy",cuisine:"Traditional",capacity: 15  ,price: 15  ,address:"738, Drake Street",event_date:"2016-08-03",image_file:"hangover.jpg",start_time:"20:00 PM ")
Event.create(title:"Con air at Lighthouse labs", description:"For the new cohort arriving today we will be putting on this event for you. I am sure many of your are as excited as we were when we first arrived. However you will soon realise that this 50 square meter room will become home for 12+ hours a day of intensive learning. You will have daily chores, your diet will probably consist of simple fast food meals from around the hood, and your exercise will be limited to foosball. Does this lack of freedom remind you of anything? Hahahaha self invlicted yet highly benfcial incarceration. In honour of our life choices we would to theme up the place and screen Con Air. We will be serving mini Jail house meals to add some sustinece to the evening. Great jail house classics like Chili and bread, and soup and toast will be on the menu throughout the evening. After the movie we can Breakout to the bars and cause havoc around town like I am sure the senior cohort will do on Thursday.",movie_genre:"Drama",cuisine:"Traditional",capacity: 100 ,price: 0 ,address:"128, Hasting Street",event_date:"2016-06-22",image_file:"lighthouse.jpg",start_time:"19:00 PM")